      even as a secondary component;
   d) Commercial services whose value is directly derived from
      the functionality of this Software.

   The Software is and must remain free of charge to end users.

3. COMMERCIAL LICENSING BY CONTRACT

   The integration or distribution of this Software in any
   commercial product, service, or context — even if the Software
   itself is not sold directly — REQUIRES prior, explicit, and
   formalized authorization from the original author.

   Such authorization must be obtained through a COMMERCIAL
   LICENSING AGREEMENT signed by the original author ("inrryoff"),
   negotiated individually before any commercial use begins.

   Without such an agreement:

   a) No use in any paid, freemium, or monetized product is
      permitted, regardless of the form of monetization;
   b) No integration into SaaS platforms, commercially distributed
      applications, or paid services is authorized;
   c) Prior contact or stated intent alone does not substitute
      for a formally signed agreement.

   To request a commercial licensing agreement, please contact:
   GitHub:   https://github.com/inrryoff
   Telegram: https://t.me/inrryoff

4. MODIFICATIONS AND DERIVATIVE WORKS

   Modifications are welcome, provided that:

   a) The derivative work is not commercialized (per section 2),
      except under a contract as per section 3;
   b) The derivative work is publicly distributed under this
